OpenSim::AbstractMuscle

AbstractMuscle Class Reference

#include <AbstractMuscle.h>

Inheritance diagram for AbstractMuscle:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

A base class representing a SIMM muscle.

It adds data and methods to AbstractActuator, but does not implement all of the necessary methods, so it is abstract too.

Author:
Peter Loan

Frank C. Anderson

Version:
1.0
